&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🏆 🎉 🏆 &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://octopusmoney.com/octopus-money-named-advice-firm-of-the-year-at-money-marketing-awards&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;We&#39;re proud to announce we&#39;ve won Advice firm of the year at the Money Marketing Awards&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;🏆 🎉 🏆&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Backend Engineer with solid Golang and database skills to help us build the scalable operations, technology, and processes needed to transform 5 million lives by making high-quality financial support affordable and accessible to employees everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;
