&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with the tech leads and other Engineers on deciding future technologies and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with modern and new technologies and frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working in an Agile team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building relationships with product and devops&lt;/li&gt;
