&lt;p&gt;Help us build the best customer support team in financial services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everyone knows the legendary customer service that made Octopus Energy famous.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&#39;s exactly what we&#39;re building at Octopus Money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe financial services doesn&#39;t have to feel slow, complicated or frustrating. We want every interaction to leave clients feeling understood, supported and confident that someone genuinely cares about getting the right outcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an ambitious Senior Customer Support Executive to join us on a 12-month maternity cover contract. You&#39;ll become one of the most experienced members of our Customer Support team, helping deliver exceptional service every day while playing an important role in shaping how our support function evolves as we grow.&lt;/p&gt;
