&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re excited by building something exceptional rather than simply maintaining the status quo, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Customer Support Team Lead is going on maternity leave, creating an opportunity for an experienced financial services professional to step into a senior operational role within a small, high-performing team.&lt;/p&gt;
